7:["$","main",null,{"className":"article-page","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BlogPosting\",\"headline\":\"Comparing Your Relationship to Couples Online (and How to Stop)\",\"description\":\"Their highlight reel is not your real life. A practical way out of the comparison spiral.\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-06-26\",\"mainEntityOfPage\":\"https://bexhearts.com/blog/stop-comparing-your-relationship-online\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Bexhearts\",\"url\":\"https://bexhearts.com\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Bexhearts\",\"url\":\"https://bexhearts.com\"}}"}}],["$","article",null,{"className":"article-shell","children":[["$","$L12",null,{"href":"/blog","className":"back-link","children":[["$","svg",null,{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-arrow-left","aria-hidden":"true","children":[["$","path","1l729n",{"d":"m12 19-7-7 7-7"}],["$","path","x3x0zl",{"d":"M19 12H5"}],"$undefined"]}],"Blog"]}],["$","header",null,{"className":"article-hero","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"section-kicker","children":"Dating"}],["$","h1",null,{"children":"Comparing Your Relationship to Couples Online (and How to Stop)"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Their highlight reel is not your real life. A practical way out of the comparison spiral."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"article-meta","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-06-26","children":"2026-06-26"}],["$","span",null,{"children":[4," min read"]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"article-content","children":[["$","section","0",{"children":["$undefined",[["$","p","Comparison usually sneaks in through the phone: engagement photos, anniversary trips, a couple who seems effortlessly devout. Thirty seconds of scrolling and your own good, ordinary relationship suddenly looks like a deficit.",{"children":"Comparison usually sneaks in through the phone: engagement photos, anniversary trips, a couple who seems effortlessly devout. Thirty seconds of scrolling and your own good, ordinary relationship suddenly looks like a deficit."}],["$","p","The problem is not that their life is fake. It is that you are comparing their curated peak to your uncurated average, and no relationship survives that math.",{"children":"The problem is not that their life is fake. It is that you are comparing their curated peak to your uncurated average, and no relationship survives that math."}]]]}],["$","section","Audit the feed, honestly",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Audit the feed, honestly"}],[["$","p","Notice which accounts reliably leave you feeling behind, and mute them without ceremony. This is not bitterness; it is stewardship of your attention.",{"children":"Notice which accounts reliably leave you feeling behind, and mute them without ceremony. This is not bitterness; it is stewardship of your attention."}],["$","p","Then replace the input: for every comparison trigger you remove, add one practice that turns you toward your actual partner — a gratitude named out loud, a question asked, a prayer prayed.",{"children":"Then replace the input: for every comparison trigger you remove, add one practice that turns you toward your actual partner — a gratitude named out loud, a question asked, a prayer prayed."}]]]}],["$","section","Keep score of your own story instead",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Keep score of your own story instead"}],[["$","p","The antidote to watching other people’s highlight reels is building your own record — not for an audience, but for the two of you. Answered prayers, milestones, small faithful streaks.",{"children":"The antidote to watching other people’s highlight reels is building your own record — not for an audience, but for the two of you. Answered prayers, milestones, small faithful streaks."}],"$L13"]]}]]}],"$L14","$L15"]}]]}]
